            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[并不简单]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_bingbujiandan-9955880b30.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>转发周知！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%88%B4%E9%98%B2%E8%93%9D%E5%85%89%E7%9C%BC%E9%95%9C%E8%83%BD%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E7%9C%BC%E7%9D%9B%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%88%B4%E9%98%B2%E8%93%9D%E5%85%89%E7%9C%BC%E9%95%9C%E8%83%BD%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E7%9C%BC%E7%9D%9B%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#戴防蓝光眼镜能保护眼睛吗#</span></a> 】为了保护视力，要不要配一副防蓝光眼镜呢？专家表示：蓝光存在于自然光线中，其中有一个波段对眼睛确实是有损伤，但是需要达到一定的时间和剂量效应，生活中的蓝光并不会对眼睛有多大损伤。一些合格的电子产品本身已经屏蔽掉了一部分有害的蓝光，因此并不需要刻意戴防蓝光眼镜。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%9B%B6%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%E6%8A%A4%E7%9C%BC%E5%B1%8F%E7%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%89%E7%94%A8%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%9B%B6%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%E6%8A%A4%E7%9C%BC%E5%B1%8F%E7%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%89%E7%94%A8%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#零风险护眼屏真的有用吗#</span></a> <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4904902409781281" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">CCTV生活圈的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/orj480/713e54f1ly1he9ddtecr1j21hc0u0gqe.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/XEmtQ0YClx085GC3t2Ji01041200GT7z0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1685006397&amp;ssig=SMJDabRe61&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/xWNIRhwWlx085GC2KiRi01041200gT8d0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1685006397&amp;ssig=QH%2FkpROIC2&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/t0gsn3yUlx085GC2ruxW010412009fUH0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1685006397&amp;ssig=wMHdYrZCEq&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4904902409781281&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
